OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782456514
OL,3,CUnions demand urgent investment in
OL,4,Cschool buildings as heatwave forces
OL,5,Cclosures
OL,7,FUnions have urged the government to
OL,8,Finvest in the UK's ageing educational
OL,9,Fbuildings after schools were forced to
OL,10,Fclose or partially close due to this
OL,11,Fweek's record-breaking temperatures.
OL,13,FThe National Education Union has
OL,14,Fwritten to Bridget Phillipson,
OL,15,FSecretary of State for Education,
OL,16,Fcalling for education buildings to be
OL,17,Fretrofitted or upgraded to help adapt
OL,18,Fto climate change.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782456514
OL,3,CUnions demand urgent investment in
OL,4,Cschool buildings as heatwave forces
OL,5,Cclosures
OL,7,FWednesday was the UK's hottest June
OL,8,Fday on record, with a provisional
OL,9,Ftemperature of 36.1C in Gosport,
OL,10,FHampshire. The Met Office has extended
OL,11,Fits red warning for extreme heat until
OL,12,F9pm on Friday for London and parts of
OL,13,Fsouth-east England.
OL,15,FThe UK's infrastructure has been under
OL,16,Fconsiderable pressure during the hot
OL,17,Fspell, with schools, hospitals and
OL,18,Fpublic transport particularly affected
OL,19,Fby the extreme heat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782456514
OL,3,CUnions demand urgent investment in
OL,4,Cschool buildings as heatwave forces
OL,5,Cclosures
OL,7,FCharities and campaigners have been
OL,8,Fwarning this week of the dangers to
OL,9,Fvulnerable people, including the
OL,10,Felderly and young children, of extreme
OL,11,Fheat, with people urged to take
OL,12,Fprecautions where they can.
OL,14,FAt least 1,000 schools across the
OL,15,Fcountry have been closed or partially
OL,16,Fclosed as a result of the rare red
OL,17,Fheat warning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782456514
OL,3,CUnions demand urgent investment in
OL,4,Cschool buildings as heatwave forces
OL,5,Cclosures
OL,7,FIn Somerset, more than 200 schools are
OL,8,Fshut or operating on more limited
OL,9,Fopening hours, while more than 100
OL,10,Fschools will be at least partly closed
OL,11,Fin Bristol, Gloucestershire,
OL,12,FOxfordshire, Buckinghamshire and
OL,13,FHampshire.
OL,15,FOther schools are making adjustments,
OL,16,Fsuch as relaxing uniform rules, to
OL,17,Fhelp keep students and staff safe and
OL,18,Fcomfortable.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782456514
OL,3,CUnions demand urgent investment in
OL,4,Cschool buildings as heatwave forces
OL,5,Cclosures
OL,7,FNEU general secretary Daniel Kebede
OL,8,Fsaid the government's pledge to make
OL,9,Fschools fit for purpose, on its
OL,10,Fcurrent trajectory, will not be
OL,11,Fcompleted until the year 2246.
OL,13,FIn his letter to Phillipson, the NEU
OL,14,Fsaid, "every school closure this week
OL,15,Fis a direct consequence of successive
OL,16,Fgovernments failing to invest in the
OL,17,FUK's school estate".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782456514
OL,3,CUnions demand urgent investment in
OL,4,Cschool buildings as heatwave forces
OL,5,Cclosures
OL,7,FHe continued: "Many of our school
OL,8,Fbuildings consist of either
OL,9,Funinsulated Victorian structures or
OL,10,Fpoorly insulated 1960s and 1970s
OL,11,Fsystem-built blocks.
OL,13,F"I am writing to you to call for
OL,14,Furgent investment for education
OL,15,Fbuildings to be retrofitted or
OL,16,Fupgraded to help adapt to climate
OL,17,Fchange. Schools need to be more
OL,18,Fresilient to heat and cold, be more
OL,19,Fenergy efficient, and ultimately
OL,20,Ftransition to net zero.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782456514
OL,3,CUnions demand urgent investment in
OL,4,Cschool buildings as heatwave forces
OL,5,Cclosures
OL,7,F"Much more needs to be done to help
OL,8,Fbetter prepare our education system
OL,9,Ffor the climate emergency. Greater
OL,10,Finvestment is needed to make all
OL,11,Fschools resilient to this type of
OL,12,Fextreme weather, which is only going
OL,13,Fto become more common."
OL,15,FSir Keir Starmer said schools have to
OL,16,Fdecide for themselves whether it is
OL,17,Fright to close early.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782456514
OL,3,CUnions demand urgent investment in
OL,4,Cschool buildings as heatwave forces
OL,5,Cclosures
OL,7,FAsked if it was right that children's
OL,8,Feducation suffers because of the
OL,9,Fextreme weather, the outgoing prime
OL,10,Fminister said: "It is very hot, and
OL,11,Fobviously schools will have to take
OL,12,Fthe appropriate measures, and each
OL,13,Fschool will gauge for themselves the
OL,14,Fmeasures that are appropriate.
OL,16,F"But it is important that we as a
OL,17,Fgovernment coordinate this across the
OL,18,Fcountry, and actually with all of the
OL,19,Fcountries within the United Kingdom,
OL,20,Fwhich is what we're doing."
OL,26,@rD@POUxD@AOU|D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782456514
OL,3,CUnions demand urgent investment in
OL,4,Cschool buildings as heatwave forces
OL,5,Cclosures
OL,7,FCobra meetings are taking place "at
OL,8,Fthe official level", Starmer said,
OL,9,Fadding: "Obviously, it falls to me and
OL,10,Fothers to say, take care, be sensible
OL,11,Fwith precautions, and schools are
OL,12,Fgoing to have to decide. They are
OL,13,Fdeciding."
OL,15,FCare settings, too, are struggling to
OL,16,Fcope, with reports of patients on
OL,17,Fgeriatric wards facing temperatures of
OL,18,Fup to 35C, according to the Royal
OL,19,FCollege of Physicians (RCP).
OL,26,@oD@aOUpD@SO]qD@IOUuD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782456514
OL,3,CUnions demand urgent investment in
OL,4,Cschool buildings as heatwave forces
OL,5,Cclosures
OL,7,FThe temperatures were also affecting
OL,8,Ftesting laboratories and machines used
OL,9,Fto treat cancer, the RCP said.
OL,11,FDr Hilary Williams, RCP clinical vice-
OL,12,Fpresident, said that the impact of
OL,13,Fheatwaves on staff in hospitals
OL,14,F"cannot be overstated".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782456514
OL,3,CUnions demand urgent investment in
OL,4,Cschool buildings as heatwave forces
OL,5,Cclosures
OL,7,F"It is not as simple as buying fans,
OL,8,Fwhich can present a fire risk when
OL,9,Fused alongside oxygen, and may
OL,10,Fincrease the spread of infection. The
OL,11,FNHS is already facing enormous
OL,12,Fpressure from rising demand and
OL,13,Fworkforce shortages. Coupled with an
OL,14,Fageing estate, these challenges
OL,15,Fintensify during extreme weather," Dr
OL,16,FWilliams said.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782456514
OL,3,CUnions demand urgent investment in
OL,4,Cschool buildings as heatwave forces
OL,5,Cclosures
OL,7,FShe continued: "But this must be
OL,8,Fmatched by system-level change `
OL,9,Fstrengthening infrastructure and
OL,10,Fembedding resilience into NHS reform.
OL,11,FBuildings must be upgraded to
OL,12,Fwithstand extreme heat and other
OL,13,Fclimate risks."
OL,15,FAlmost 1.6 million children, including
OL,16,Fmore than 70,000 babies, are living in
OL,17,Foverheated homes in England, according
OL,18,Fto campaigners, who called for "urgent
OL,19,Faction" to ensure housing can be kept
OL,20,Fat safe temperatures.
OL,26,@zD@`OU{D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782456514
OL,3,CUnions demand urgent investment in
OL,4,Cschool buildings as heatwave forces
OL,5,Cclosures
OL,7,FThe National Housing Federation (NHF)
OL,8,Fwarned that with warmer weather
OL,9,Fbecoming more frequent, it is becoming
OL,10,F"impossible"for parents to ensure
OL,11,Ftheir homes are comfortable.
OL,13,FThe Climate Change Committee has
OL,14,Fpreviously suggested that hotter
OL,15,Ftemperatures could result in 92% of
OL,16,Fexisting homes overheating, with a
OL,17,Fprediction that by the middle of the
OL,18,Fcentury, the UK's climate "will be
OL,19,Fmuch more extreme than today".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782456514
OL,3,CUnions demand urgent investment in
OL,4,Cschool buildings as heatwave forces
OL,5,Cclosures
OL,7,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,8,Fadvises that children can be at risk
OL,9,Ffrom hot weather because of their
OL,10,Fphysiology, behaviours and activity
OL,11,Flevels and suggests cooling a child
OL,12,Fsuffering from heat exhaustion by
OL,13,Fsponging or spraying them with cool
OL,14,Fwater and putting cold packs on their
OL,15,Fneck and armpits, or wrapping them in
OL,16,Fa cool, wet sheet and using a fan.
